Margaret Bamgbose (amuru Ọktoba 19, 1993) bu onye oso egwu na ogige Naijiria nke ọpụrụiche na 400 mita
Ọ bụ onye iri na otu n'oge niile America na Mahadum Notre Dame.
Bamgbose gbara ọsọ 400 mita na asọmpi mba ụwa nke afọ 2017 na nke iri abụọ n'oge 52.23.
Bamgbose gbara ọkpụ ụzọ n'ọsọ 4 × 400 m relay maka Nigeria na asọmpi ime ụlọ nke ụwa nke afọ 2016
Ndị otu nke mejupụtara Bamgbose, Regina George, Tameka Jameson na Ada Benjamin Agbagharala oghere otu egwuregwu n'ebe nke anọ
O banyere nke atọ n'asọmpi Naijiria nke 2016 n'azụ Patience George na Omolara Omotoso wee si otú ahụ mechie ọkwa ya maka asọmpi Rio Olympik

N'afọ 2016, Bamgbose gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Notre Dame wee nweta akara ugo mmụta na njikwa teknụzụ ozi sitere na mahadum Mendoza College of Business
Onye America niile ugboro iri na otu, o debere kọleji kacha mma na 200 m na 400 m na 2016
Na 2014 na 2015, ọ gbachara n'ebe nke isii na NCAA Outdoor finals na  oge abụọ
O mekwara agba nke ikpeazụ n'afọ 2016 wee gụchaa n'ebe nke anọ
Ọ bụkwa onye mmeri ACC Indoor 400 Mita 2015.
A mụrụ Bamgbose na United States na nne na nna si Naijiria, Sunday na Afusatu Bamgbose bụ ndị si Abeokuta na ndịda ọdịda anyanwụ Nigeria
O nwere ụmụnne abụọ, nwanne nwanyị tọrọ ya na nwanne nwoke ọ tọrọ
Ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Evanston Township High School, Illinois
Bamgbose malitere dịka onye na awu ihe mgbochi n'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na n'oge mahadum mbụ tupu ọ mara nke ọma na asọmpi 400 mita
